{"tid":2013984,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港麻雀問題 [平時有打開入]","createTime":"2020-05-12T16:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T03:05:39.000Z","uid":146505,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"9562a5c9126f3aef37f99073072e8f4ac51675c9","tid":2013984,"uid":146505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:34:03.000Z","msg":"大家平時打香港牌三番起糊嘅時候<br />\n會唔會做 平糊正花自摸 嘅雞糊<br />\n啲牌唔靚或者適合我就會做<br />\n因為雖然唔大 <br />\n但可攻可守 可以避免好多出銃嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n但係我有朋友同我打打下屌鳩我做雞糊<br />\n話咩阻人發達又不利己<br />\n下 唔通打曬你要嘅牌俾你呀<br />\n即係啲牌爛到點都要瘋狂進攻衝牌？<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家平時打三番起糊嘅時候會唔會做雞<br />\n係我朋友戇鳩定我咁樣真係唔好？"},{"pid":"084c3973e72a110058d21e4248504d3b62387885","tid":2013984,"uid":210009,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"on9食到咪得"},{"pid":"1d52370f607031c20557dced935de6260ada90c7","tid":2013984,"uid":72470,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:36:38.000Z","msg":"你朋友on99 你咁打完全正確"},{"pid":"083a72423b436325724dacf5c41cef9a0b3949f6","tid":2013984,"uid":152147,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"你同佢講出比你雞糊總好過出鋪爆棚比人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd21cdd9ecd6797e177a59c8ae9ad62beaa3b285","tid":2013984,"uid":146505,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"084c3973e72a110058d21e4248504d3b62387885","tid":2013984,"uid":210009,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"on9食到咪得"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"我個frd嬲到話<br />\n一係就食三番雞糊當詐糊<br />\n一係就唔同我打"},{"pid":"1ad31515f2276ab2f5e02abf48b5c87cad648a80","tid":2013984,"uid":308167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:38:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b053d10810f180dbcda2631a396529dd6c059134","tid":2013984,"uid":229397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT