=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食到咪得<br />\n之前試過打成日都剩係做雞糊<br />\n見到其他人係度砌大牌<br />\n我就係咁食糊<br />\n個感覺都不知幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"你對手果日弱啫 人地好摸手嘅話 你下下三番都隨時唔夠人地快 兼且痾突"},{"pid":"9b46d78b564bafff4b046c828056e956ed8f3286","tid":2013984,"uid":197584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:49:19.000Z","msg":"平糊正花自摸三番有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔明點解係雞糊<br />\n雞糊係又上又碰喎"},{"pid":"3edf95047853f32961305337281b77cf0a8c53df","tid":2013984,"uid":2716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:50:16.000Z","msg":"平糊邊係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常4441/445+正花先會考慮<br />\n無花搏自摸平糊太大風險<br />\n如果一邊有6或以上通常都會考慮混/清一色先<br />\n4對或以上就對對"},{"pid":"a8c48371520041eadd6fb1a45e15a2abadc46e84","tid":2013984,"uid":93199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"兩隻正花平糊人打又食得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n碰到雙番東南西北其他求其然後自摸又食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺明人地大牌比你破壞左發脾氣<br />\n用雞糊破壞人地大牌最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d241a25774d8b48baa0d73881a73d7de2c6c7ff","tid":2013984,"uid":145017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:52:15.000Z","msg":"如果真屌牌品有問題而且其實都唔係好fd<br />\n可能打牌for娛樂但你都無理由明知咩都無都唔做3番，而且3番其實都唔係真係話想食就食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ce964ac0c95c4b5b266238db9fd93cd5b36545","tid":2013984,"uid":134589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:54:47.000Z","msg":"只會屌鳩人做對對糊 其餘冇問題"},{"pid":"20fe855395f954cf55a717e1a30e865496bb6df4","tid":2013984,"uid":146505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d241a25774d8b48baa0d73881a73d7de2c